ects seems to be absent in CC, enabling\nmeteorite delivery even at high speeds, though in the form of only small\nfragments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Feb 2019 10:26:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-05"}
