es in the Marenostrum-IV platform. The\nparallel implementation of the AgFEM method is available in the large-scale\nfinite element package FEMPAR.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Feb 2019 13:24:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Aug 2019 06:05:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-20"}
